<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4632; padding: 2rem;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Your referral worked! 🎉</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
    Hi <%= @referrer.first_name %>,
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Great news — <strong><%= @referee.first_name %></strong> just paid for their gooi subscription using your referral code.
    You've earned <strong>R50 off</strong> your next subscription renewal.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Your discount will be applied automatically next time you resubscribe — no code needed.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Know anyone else who'd love to gooi? Share your referral code: <strong><%= @referrer.referral_code %></strong>
  </p>

  <p style="margin: 2rem 0;">
    <a href="<%= referrals_url %>"
       style="background-color: #FBB718; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
      View My Referrals
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Thanks for spreading the word! 🌱</p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Kristen</p>
  <%= image_tag image_url('email-signature.png'), alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
</div>
